frikadelliemad 137479013214 "2016-01-17 14:08:03 GMT" https://frikadelliemad.tumblr.com/post/137479013214/interesting-facts-victoria-justice "Victoria Justice is an American multi-talented celebrity that particularly focuses on acting
column4: and voice acting. She was born on the 19th of February
column7: USA. She started her acting career in the year 2003 when she was 10 years old and appeared on the comedy-drama series Gilmore Girls in a guest role. After that appearance
column8: Victoria decided to pursue her Hollywood calling
column9: which made her parents Zack and Serene decide to move to Los Angeles.Nowadays
column10: Victoria appears as one of the brightest stars in the industry. And luckily
column11: she possesses a body with a great form—without doing anything! According to her
column12: she doesn’t go to the gym and spend time doing intensive workouts. With her busy schedule
column13: it seems difficult for her to do so. What she just basically does is move her body by dancing and performing whenever she’s on rehearsals
column15: and other shows. She says dancing is her only source of workout. However
column16: she’s taking a consideration of hiring a personal trainer to develop some muscles in the future.And how about her diet? Well
column17: the young star admits she does not really care about calories and carbs. And she’s not into counting every calorie like most women do. She also adds that she’s not the one who does the cooking
column18: so perhaps this is one of the reasons why she doesn’t gain weight. Food temptations seem to be out of her way." True text
